name: Guest House
description: An newly engaged couple's buys their dream house but it comes with one small catch, a perennial party animal who lives in the guesthouse.

review.author: filmmakersis
review.heading: I love Pauly Shore! But.....
review.reviewBody: I was excited to see Pauly Shore and don't regret paying to rent this because at least the money will go to the film crew who worked hard. That being said, this movie has nothing to offer and is empty and the lead actors playing the young couple are so utterly dull and unlikeable. But the worst offense of this film is that: IT IS NOT FUNNY. Not one second. Really bummed me out because I needed some funny.
